metadata.name: Humpback whales
metadata.description:
Witness the unparalleled beauty of the ocean through a mesmerizing 1/1 video piece. Immerse yourself in the water, feeling its raw energy and discovering something new with each viewing. Experience the graceful presence of two humpback whales, adding an enchanting element to this original and captivating creation. Let the ocean's timeless wonders unfold before you, inviting you to embark on a visual journey like no other.

Location: Ben Buckler, Sydney, Australia
Format: 1080 × 1920 video
Duration: 00:31
